{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_05.gif?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/ItsTimeToBreakFree.png?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_01.gif?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Towerbolt is a precision platformer with an emphasis on speed and fluid ascending movement.  Set in the far future where robots are waging war against humanity, play as a Bolter, an augmented half human, half robot super soldier, and break out of a futuristic Megatower prison!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/YouVSTheTower.png?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_02.gif?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each floor of the Megatower is equipped with deadly security lasers that will chase you as you ascend the tower.  Outsprint these lethal lasers every floor while avoiding other security measures on your climb to the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/FluidAscendingMovement.png?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_03.gif?t=1740433935\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Towerbolt is designed to be easy to pick up with a simple one button control scheme, but leaves lots of room for mastery with a high skill ceiling.\u00a0 Utilize the Bolter Charge mechanic and chain jumps without touching to ground to charge vertical momentum to ascend faster and finish levels with lightning speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/100Floors.png?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_04.gif?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Tower spans over 100 floors and features new obstacles that will challenge and test you on your path to escape.\u00a0 Each floor is a micro platforming challenge designed to be quick to try, retry, and finish to keep you moving fast throughout the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/OtherFeatures.png?t=1740433935\" /> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optional Challenge Collectables and Personal Rankings per Floor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vibrant Neon Pixel Art Aesthetic </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A mysterious sci-fi story set in the far future </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2559220?t=1740433935","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2559220?t=1740433935","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740433935","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740433935","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2624390,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_05.gif?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/ItsTimeToBreakFree.png?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_01.gif?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Towerbolt is a precision platformer with an emphasis on speed and fluid ascending movement.  Set in the far future where robots are waging war against humanity, play as a Bolter, an augmented half human, half robot super soldier, and break out of a futuristic Megatower prison!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/YouVSTheTower.png?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_02.gif?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each floor of the Megatower is equipped with deadly security lasers that will chase you as you ascend the tower.  Outsprint these lethal lasers every floor while avoiding other security measures on your climb to the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/FluidAscendingMovement.png?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_03.gif?t=1740433935\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Towerbolt is designed to be easy to pick up with a simple one button control scheme, but leaves lots of room for mastery with a high skill ceiling.\u00a0 Utilize the Bolter Charge mechanic and chain jumps without touching to ground to charge vertical momentum to ascend faster and finish levels with lightning speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/100Floors.png?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/Towerbolt_GIF_04.gif?t=1740433935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Tower spans over 100 floors and features new obstacles that will challenge and test you on your path to escape.\u00a0 Each floor is a micro platforming challenge designed to be quick to try, retry, and finish to keep you moving fast throughout the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/extras/OtherFeatures.png?t=1740433935\" /> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optional Challenge Collectables and Personal Rankings per Floor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vibrant Neon Pixel Art Aesthetic </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A mysterious sci-fi story set in the far future </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["bordenary"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559220/header.jpg?t=1740433935","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257098746,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257098746/movie480.mp4?t=1740433259","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257098746/movie_max.mp4?t=1740433259"},"name":"Release Window Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257098746/50a206e65ece77f1f81eeeee24c66b51ab0fea14/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1740433259","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257098746/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1740433259","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257098746/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1740433259"}}],"name":"Towerbolt","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10 and above<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 1.2 ghz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 512 mb video memory<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 10<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 25 MB available space</li></ul>"},"platforms":{"linux":false,"mac":false,"windows":true},"publishers":["bordenary"],"ratings":{"dejus":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Viol\u00eancia","rating":"10","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"10","use_age_gate":"0"},"steam_germany":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Gewalt","rating":"12","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"12","use_age_gate":"0"}},"release_date":{"coming_soon":true,"date":"2025"},"required_age":0,"screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_full":"https://s